{"tid":2285400,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"郭家麒：有公民黨成員曾期望美方外交交涉　勿輕易制裁香港","createTime":"2020-11-14T05:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T15:15:38.000Z","uid":37112,"like":8,"dislike":225,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"37756381e7c2e2a63c8e671e4dab797d81f08d6e","tid":2285400,"uid":37112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T05:29:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559980-20201114.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559980-20201114.htm&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy4ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=bbc433d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559980-20201114.htm&h=1d3d51f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559980-20201114.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n郭家麒：有成員曾期望美方外交交涉　勿輕易制裁香港<br />\n2020-11-14 HKT 11:25<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被取消立法會議員資格的郭家麒表示，有成員曾經向美方表示不要輕易制裁香港。<br />\n<br />\n他出席一個電台節目時回應有說法指公民黨要求美國制裁香港，他表示<strong><span class=\"red\">有成員曾經在美國，向美方表示不要輕易制裁香港，因為香港不想受經濟打擊，只是當時沒有向外透露，又說公民黨都希望香港亂局會停，希望對方以外交途徑與中方或香港交涉。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n出席同一節目的民主派會議召集人胡志偉表示，如果因為犯錯誤招致別人制裁，再找代罪羔羊，只是反映政權的橫蠻無理。至於有說法認為由於民主派拉布，令4名議員被取消資格，他重申個多月來，民主派一直根據議事規則點算人數，是合規矩。"},{"pid":"92fd9cdeb1dc51451d69e29b1cebd797c0a267cf","tid":2285400,"uid":77196,"like":75,"dislike":2,"score":73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"咪撚信唐英年啦，條友弱智的"},{"pid":"7ce8ddb485231832eb0a786009859f508cdd0de1","tid":2285400,"uid":37112,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T05:36:35.000Z","msg":"泛民：美國請勿制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe55d006176bd67080e7821e8f7ef10c5f9fa08","tid":2285400,"uid":41658,"like":59,"dislike":5,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-1